(10, 0, 0, 'Khi cng casino trong t hp 4 t USD  Qung Nam', '', '', '', 'khoi-cong-casino-trong-to-hop-4-ty-usd-o-quang-nam', '', '', '', 'Thng tin d n casino trong t hp 4 t USD ti Qung Nam chnh thc khi cng c Coteccons a ra. Cng trnh d kin hon thnh sau 19 thng thi cng.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">&nbsp;Th&ocirc;ng tin d &aacute;n casino trong t hp 4 t USD ti Qung Nam ch&iacute;nh thc khi c&ocirc;ng c Coteccons a ra. C&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh d kin ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh sau 19 th&aacute;ng thi c&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ty c phn x&acirc;y dng Coteccons cho bit &atilde; khi c&ocirc;ng d &aacute;n casino vi tr gi&aacute; hp ng x&acirc;y lp l&agrave; 7.000 t ng. Coteccons cho hay doanh nghip n&agrave;y &atilde; thng thu d &aacute;n khi vt qua nhiu nh&agrave; thu quc t kh&aacute;c. D kin, c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh s ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh sau 19 th&aacute;ng thi c&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n<p>D &aacute;n t hp kh&aacute;ch sn, khu ngh dng, casino... Nam Hi An c x&acirc;y dng vi din t&iacute;ch khong 1.000 ha vi nm tr&ecirc;n a b&agrave;n 3 x&atilde; Duy Hi, Duy Ngha (huyn Duy Xuy&ecirc;n) v&agrave; x&atilde; B&igrave;nh Dng (huyn Thng B&igrave;nh), tnh Qung Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Phn mi c khi c&ocirc;ng l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh casino vi tr gi&aacute; vn u t x&acirc;y lp khong 7.000 t ng.</p>\r\n<p>D &aacute;n n&agrave;y c&oacute; v tr&iacute; gn s&acirc;n bay quc t &agrave; Nng, c&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng xa ph c Hi An v&agrave; th&aacute;nh a M Sn cng nh khu d tr sinh quyn th gii C&ugrave; Lao Ch&agrave;m. D &aacute;n cng l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh c&oacute; vn u t ln nht tnh Qung Nam hin nay.</p>\r\n<p>D kin &acirc;y s l&agrave; t hp gii tr&iacute; kh&aacute;ch sn, du lch, casino&hellip; ln th 2 Vit Nam c x&acirc;y dng. Ch u t d &aacute;n Casino Hi An l&agrave; li&ecirc;n doanh gia VinaCapital v&agrave; 2 tp o&agrave;n ln l&agrave; Chow-Tai-Fook (HongKong) v&agrave; The Suncity Group (Macau).</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Khi c&ocirc;ng casino trong t hp 4 t USD  Qung Nam h&igrave;nh nh 2" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_17/images1706148_phoi_canh_mot_tieu_khu_cua_du_an_2_1_1460794694792.jpg" alt="Khoi cong casino trong to hop 4 ty USD o Quang Nam hinh anh 2" width="660" height="371" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<p>&nbsp;Phi cnh d &aacute;n casino mi c khi c&ocirc;ng.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>T hp d &aacute;n c cp giy chng nhn u t v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 12/2010, do li&ecirc;n doanh gia VinaCapital v&agrave; VinaLand v&agrave; Tp o&agrave;n Genting Berhad (Malaysia) hp t&aacute;c u t. Trong &oacute;, VinaCapital s u t 80% vn d &aacute;n, tng ng gn 3,2 t USD, c&ograve;n Genting Berhad u t 20% vn. Sau &oacute; v&agrave;o khong cui nm 2012, Getting Berhad bt ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o r&uacute;t lui.</p>\r\n<p>n u nm 2015, &ocirc;ng  Xu&acirc;n Din, Trng ban Qun l&yacute; Khu kinh t m Chu Lai, x&aacute;c nhn th&ocirc;ng tin Tp o&agrave;n Chow Tai Fook (Hong Kong) c&ugrave;ng vi Sun City (Macau) &atilde; c chn l&agrave; ch u t cho d &aacute;n Nam Hi an thay th Genting Berhad ca Malaysia. Tp o&agrave;n Chow Tai Fook g&acirc;y bt ng khi nm gi c phn chi phi ti d &aacute;n thay v&igrave; VinaCapital nh trc &acirc;y.</p>\r\n<br class="Apple-interchange-newline" />\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_17/map__quangnam_zing.jpg" alt="Khoi cong casino trong to hop 4 ty USD o Quang Nam hinh anh 3" width="1353" height="801" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', '', '59106912.jpg', '59106912_300x200.jpg', 1, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 21),
(11, 0, 0, 'HoREA: Cha thy bt k cun s  thc t no ca condotel', '', '', '', 'horea-chua-thay-bat-ky-cuon-so-do-thuc-te-nao-cua-condotel', '', '', '', 'Hip hi Bt ng sn TP.HCM (HoREA) lo ngi loi hnh condotel ang c du hiu pht trin nng t bin. iu ny c th dn n tnh trng th trng bi thc cung vt cu.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">Hip hi Bt ng sn TP.HCM (HoREA) lo ngi loi h&igrave;nh condotel ang c&oacute; du hiu ph&aacute;t trin n&oacute;ng t bin. iu n&agrave;y c&oacute; th dn n t&igrave;nh trng th trng bi thc cung vt cu.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<p>HoREA va c&oacute; vn bn kin ngh c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p nhm ph&aacute;t trin bn vng th trng cn h du lch ngh dng (bit th bin, cn h kh&aacute;ch sn - condotel) ti c&aacute;c c quan chc nng. Theo HoREA, trong nhng nm gn &acirc;y, c bit l&agrave; t 2014, tr&ecirc;n phm vi c nc &atilde; xut hin cn st u t ph&aacute;t trin condotel.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Loi h&igrave;nh condotel ph&aacute;t trin tp trung ti c&aacute;c khu vc ven bin, hi o nh V&acirc;n n, H Long, Sm Sn, &agrave; Nng, Quy Nhn, Nha Trang, Mi N&eacute;, Ph&uacute; Quc... Trong &oacute;, Nha Trang, &agrave; Nng, Ph&uacute; Quc l&agrave; 3 a b&agrave;n ang ph&aacute;t trin n&oacute;ng nht loi h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2016, tng ngun cung cn h condotel &atilde; l&ecirc;n n 16.000 cn. Trong giai on 2017-2019, d kin trung b&igrave;nh mi nm s c&oacute; khong 27.000-29.000 cn h condotel c m b&aacute;n, vi din t&iacute;ch cn h khong tr&ecirc;n di 45 m2.</p>\r\n<h3>Mp m cam kt li nhun v&agrave; quyn s hu</h3>\r\n<p>HoREA ch ra mt s vn  trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t trin c&aacute;c d &aacute;n condotel trong thi gian va qua.</p>\r\n<p>u ti&ecirc;n l&agrave; vic l&atilde;nh o nhiu a phng &atilde; mi gi u t v&agrave; to iu kin v qu t, v th tc h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh  thu h&uacute;t c&aacute;c d &aacute;n condotel phc v du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Th hai,  u t d &aacute;n condotel, c&aacute;c ch u t ch yu vay vn ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng. Ngo&agrave;i ra ch u t c&ograve;n tn dng ngun vn nh&agrave; thu  x&acirc;y dng c s h tng ban u, thm ch&iacute; l&agrave; ch&iacute;nh c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh condotel ti khi b&aacute;n c cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng (nh&agrave; u t th cp). Nh vy, ngun vn t b ra ca nh&agrave; u t l&agrave; rt thp.</p>\r\n<p>Th ba, HoREA lo ngi chuyn ch u t b&aacute;n condotel cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng (nh&agrave; u t th cp) nhm mc &iacute;ch huy ng vn ging nh phng thc b&aacute;n nh&agrave;  h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh trong tng lai. HoREA nhn mnh hin ti ph&aacute;p lut cha cho ph&eacute;p thc hin phng thc b&aacute;n nh&agrave; h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh trong tng lai.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_17/bien_da_nang5_zing.jpg" alt="HoREA: Chua thay bat ky cuon so do thuc te nao cua condotel hinh anh 1" width="1980" height="1320" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<p>&nbsp;Nhiu d &aacute;n condotel c ch&agrave;o b&aacute;n ti &agrave; Nng. nh:&nbsp;<em>L&ecirc; Hiu.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Khi thc hin phng ph&aacute;p b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng n&agrave;y, ch u t c li rt ln v&igrave; thu hi vn u t nhanh, c&oacute; th&ecirc;m ngun vn ln, li c quyn kinh doanh condotel &atilde; b&aacute;n c. Theo &oacute; d&ugrave; phi tr li nhun cam kt cho nh&agrave; u t th cp, ch u t vn rt c&oacute; li so vi i vay ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng. Ri ro nh&agrave; u t th cp c&ugrave;ng g&aacute;nh chu, thm ch&iacute; trong c qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh khai th&aacute;c, kinh doanh sau n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<p>Th t, vic cam kt li nhun ca ch u t cng c&ograve;n mt s vn . Theo &oacute; gi&aacute; b&aacute;n condotel khong 25-45 triu ng/m2 (1-3 t ng/cn). Gi&aacute; b&aacute;n n&agrave;y cao v&agrave; tng ng vi gi&aacute; b&aacute;n cn h trung cao cp ti TP.HCM.</p>\r\n<p>Khi ch u t cam kt li nhun 8-12%/nm trong 8-12 nm th&igrave; trong gi&aacute; b&aacute;n c&oacute; th &atilde; bao gm  khon chi ph&iacute; phi tr cho cam kt li nhun n&agrave;y. Trong &oacute; c&oacute; c chi ph&iacute; trang b cn h, qun l&yacute; khai th&aacute;c kinh doanh. HoREA nhn thy c&aacute;c ch u t cng cha  cp n bin ph&aacute;p m bo cam kt li nhun.</p>\r\n<p>i vi nhng d &aacute;n condotel m&agrave; ch u t kh&ocirc;ng cam kt li nhun th&igrave; nh&agrave; u t th cp phi chu th&ecirc;m chi ph&iacute; trang b cn h, chi ph&iacute; qun l&yacute; khai th&aacute;c kinh doanh. Thm ch&iacute; nh&agrave; u t th cp c&ograve;n phi chu thu thu nhp c&aacute; nh&acirc;n khi kinh doanh cn h condotel.</p>\r\n<p>HoREA cng nhn mnh mt s ch u t &atilde; cam kt condotel s c cp giy chng nhn quyn s dng t n nh l&acirc;u d&agrave;i, kh&ocirc;ng h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh n v  i vi cn h condotel. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n hin nay vn cha thy thc t cun s  cn h condotel.</p>\r\n<p>Cam kt n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng ph&ugrave; hp vi quy nh ti khon 3 iu 126 Lut t ai &atilde; quy nh thi hn giao t, cho thu&ecirc; t i vi t chc  thc hin c&aacute;c d &aacute;n u t kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 50 nm, ti nhng v&ugrave;ng kh&oacute; khn th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 70 nm. Do vy, theo quy nh ph&aacute;p lut hin h&agrave;nh th&igrave; quyn s dng t cn h condotel trong c&aacute;c d &aacute;n du lch ngh dng c s dng t c&oacute; thi hn (theo thi hn ca d &aacute;n), v&agrave; c&oacute; th c gia hn.</p>\r\n<p>Th s&aacute;u, HoREA lo ngi trong v&agrave;i nm ti, ngun cung cn h condotel tip tc c&oacute; du hiu ph&aacute;t trin n&oacute;ng, tng t bin, c&oacute; th dn n t&igrave;nh trng bi thc cung vt cu. Thm ch&iacute; c&ograve;n xut hin th&ecirc;m "cn h hometel&rdquo;&hellip;</p>\r\n<h3>Cn c&oacute; quy chun ti&ecirc;u chun c th vi condotel</h3>\r\n<p>HoREA kin ngh mt s gii ph&aacute;p nhm ph&aacute;t trin bn vng th trng condotel, c bit l&agrave; c&aacute;c quy nh ph&aacute;p lut hin h&agrave;nh.</p>\r\n<p>Th nht, v quy chun, ti&ecirc;u chun c th i vi condotel, HoREA kin ngh B X&acirc;y dng phi hp B Vn h&oacute;a, th thao, du lch  ho&agrave;n thin b quy chun, ti&ecirc;u chun c th.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_17/bien_da_nang1_zing.jpg" alt="HoREA: Chua thay bat ky cuon so do thuc te nao cua condotel hinh anh 3" width="1980" height="1320" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<p>&nbsp;Loi h&igrave;nh condotel ph&aacute;t trin tp trung ti c&aacute;c khu vc ven bin, hi o nh V&acirc;n n, H Long, Sm Sn, &agrave; Nng, Quy Nhn, Nha Trang, Mi N&eacute;, Ph&uacute; Quc...&nbsp; nh:&nbsp;<em>L&ecirc; Hiu.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>V ph&aacute;p lut t ai, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cn lu &yacute; s c cp giy chng nhn quyn s hu cn h v&agrave; quyn s dng t c&oacute; thi hn theo thi hn s dng t ca d &aacute;n. Khi ht hn s dng t th&igrave; c gia hn nu c&oacute; nhu cu theo quy nh ca ph&aacute;p lut.</p>\r\n<p>V t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh t ai, cn c&oacute; c ch  tr&aacute;nh l&agrave;m tht tho&aacute;t ngun thu ng&acirc;n s&aacute;ch Nh&agrave; nc.</p>\r\n<p>HoREA kin ngh cho c&aacute; nh&acirc;n nc ngo&agrave;i c mua cn h condotel  u t.</p>\r\n<p>B X&acirc;y dng cng cn c&oacute; bin ph&aacute;p y&ecirc;u cu c&aacute;c ch u t d &aacute;n condotel nh c&ocirc;ng b y  th&ocirc;ng tin v quyn s hu cn h condotel v&agrave; quyn s dng t c&oacute; thi hn; c&ocirc;ng b c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p bo m thc hin cam kt li nhun; c&ocirc;ng b minh bch c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; trang b cn h, chi ph&iacute; qun l&yacute; trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh kinh doanh&hellip;</p>\r\n</div>', '', '01506117.jpg', '01506117_300x200.jpg', 2, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 7),
(20, 0, 0, 'THACO u t 120 t ng m rng cng Chu Lai', '', '', '', 'thaco-dau-tu-120-ty-dong-mo-rong-cang-chu-lai', '', '', '', 'Sau mt nm thi cng, d n m rng cng Chu Lai (Khu kinh t m Chu Lai, Qung Nam) do THACO u t  hon thnh v nng cao chui dch v logistics.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">Sau mt nm thi c&ocirc;ng, d &aacute;n m rng cng Chu Lai (Khu kinh t m Chu Lai, Qung Nam) do THACO u t &atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh v&agrave; n&acirc;ng cao chui dch v logistics.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<p>D &aacute;n m rng cng Chu Lai bao gm c&aacute;c hng mc: m rng cu cng v ph&iacute;a thng lu; m rng v&agrave; n&acirc;ng cp h thng kho b&atilde;i; ho&agrave;n thin kt cu h tng&hellip; D &aacute;n c&oacute; tng kinh ph&iacute; 120 t ng, n&acirc;ng mc u t x&acirc;y dng cng Chu Lai l&ecirc;n gn 800 t ng, t&iacute;nh t nm 2010 n nay.</p>\r\n<p>Qua 6 th&aacute;ng u nm, cng tip nhn 150 lt t&agrave;u cp cng, 200 lt lai dt t&agrave;u bin, xp d 23.000 lt TEU container v&agrave; 140.000 tn h&agrave;ng ri, tng ng 600.000 tn h&agrave;ng qua cng. Trong &oacute;, h&agrave;ng container tng 10% so vi nm 2016.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/wyhktpu/2017_08_15/Hinh_1.JPG" alt="THACO dau tu 120 ty dong mo rong cang Chu Lai hinh anh 1" width="3200" height="2400" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Cng c u t gn 800 t ng t nm 2010.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Vi 171 m m rng th&ecirc;m v ph&iacute;a thng lu, cu cng Chu Lai d&agrave;i gn 500 m,  s&acirc;u trc bn l&agrave; -9,5 m. Cu cng c&oacute; kh nng tip nhn c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c 3 t&agrave;u vi ti trng 20.000 tn, trc &acirc;y kh nng tip nhn ti a l&agrave; 2 t&agrave;u trng ti 20.000 tn.</p>\r\n<p>H thng kho b&atilde;i, xng c m rng t 71.040 m2 (nm 2016) l&ecirc;n 91.200 m2. Tng din t&iacute;ch bao gm: kho ngoi quan (57.600 m2), kho h&agrave;ng (13.440 m2), xng th&aacute;o kin kim h&agrave;ng (20.160 m2). Xng th&aacute;o kin kim h&agrave;ng l&agrave; hng mc ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n mi, c a v&agrave;o khai th&aacute;c t u nm nay.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="THACO u t 120 t ng m rng cng Chu Lai h&igrave;nh nh 2" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/wyhktpu/2017_08_15/Hinh_2.JPG" alt="THACO dau tu 120 ty dong mo rong cang Chu Lai hinh anh 2" width="3831" height="2549" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>H thng kho b&atilde;i c m rng.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Cng Chu Lai c chia l&agrave;m 3 ph&acirc;n khu ri&ecirc;ng bit bao gm: h&agrave;ng container, h&agrave;ng ri tng hp v&agrave; h&agrave;ng lng, &aacute;p ng nhu cu ca c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng t&agrave;u v&agrave; c&aacute;c doanh nghip. Khu hu cn cho h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a qua cng c&oacute; nhiu trang thit b: cu h&agrave;ng Liebherr (3 c&aacute;i), cu b&aacute;nh lp (1 c&aacute;i), xe n&acirc;ng chp (4 c&aacute;i), xe n&acirc;ng Folk Lift (35 c&aacute;i). Thit b bc xp hin i, ng b, c&ugrave;ng vi t&agrave;u lai dt v&agrave; tr&ecirc;n 20 xe u k&eacute;o c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng sut ln gi&uacute;p m bo ti u hiu qu hot ng ca cng.</p>\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh vic phc v THACO, cng c&ograve;n cung cp dch v cho c&aacute;c doanh nghip b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i: lai dt, cu h; xp d h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, kim m, lu kho; vn chuyn ng bin ni a, giao nhn vn ti v&agrave; i l&yacute; t&agrave;u bin; dch v cu bn...</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="THACO u t 120 t ng m rng cng Chu Lai h&igrave;nh nh 3" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/wyhktpu/2017_08_15/Hinh_4.jpg" alt="THACO dau tu 120 ty dong mo rong cang Chu Lai hinh anh 3" width="1274" height="715" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>C&ocirc;ng ty ng thi cung cp dch v a dng cho c&aacute;c doanh nghip b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&Ocirc;ng Trn Hu Ho&agrave;ng - Gi&aacute;m c THACO Logistics ki&ecirc;m Gi&aacute;m c Cng Chu Lai cho bit: &ldquo;Trong tng sn lng h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a qua cng, 15% l&agrave; h&agrave;ng ca hn 50 doanh nghip b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i. Ng&agrave;nh h&agrave;ng ch yu l&agrave; lng thc, n&ocirc;ng sn, ht nha, lp xe, sn, h&oacute;a cht, b&igrave;nh in, h&agrave;ng ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng... Vi vic m rng v&agrave; n&acirc;ng cp kt cu h tng v&agrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh giao nhn - vn chuyn a phng thc ca THACO Logistics, thi gian ti, lng h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a ca c&aacute;c doanh nghip b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i qua cng s tng l&ecirc;n &aacute;ng k&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p> ti u h&oacute;a chi ph&iacute; vn chuyn, THACO Logistics thc hin gim gi&aacute; 10% i vi tt c c&aacute;c loi dch v bng c&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n kt vi c&aacute;c i t&aacute;c hp l&yacute;. i vi vn ti bin, b&ecirc;n cnh c&aacute;c tuyn vn ti ni a, hin c&oacute; c&aacute;c tuyn vn ti 2 chiu Chu Lai - Fangcheng (Trung Quc), Chu Lai - Incheon (H&agrave;n Quc).</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian ti, cng s tip tc m c&aacute;c tuyn h&agrave;ng hi quc t t H&agrave;n Quc, Trung Quc, Nht Bn v trc tip Chu Lai, m ra c hi giao thng th gii, gim chi ph&iacute; vn chuyn cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; u t trong v&ugrave;ng kinh t trng im min Trung.</p>\r\n<p>Cng theo &ocirc;ng Ho&agrave;ng,  n&acirc;ng cao nng lc ca cng, trong giai on 2018 - 2020, Cng Chu Lai  xut tnh Qung Nam h tr no v&eacute;t tuyn lung n  s&acirc;u -10,7 m  c&oacute; th tip nhn t&agrave;u c&oacute; trng ti 30.000 tn. Sau nm 2010,  xut tip tc no v&eacute;t n  s&acirc;u -12m  &oacute;n t&agrave;u c&oacute; trng ti 40.000.</p>\r\n</div>', '', '78077437.jpg', '78077437_300x200.jpg', 10, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 0),
(21, 0, 0, 'ng Nai sp c thm nhiu nh  x hi?', '', '', '', 'dong-nai-sap-co-them-nhieu-nha-o-xa-hoi', '', '', '', 'Trc kin ngh ca ng Nai v p lc i vi nh  x hi, B Xy dng  trnh Chnh ph cho php tnh c p dng 2 phng n  tng din tch t lm loi hnh nh  ny.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">Trc kin ngh ca ng Nai v &aacute;p lc i vi nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi, B X&acirc;y dng &atilde; tr&igrave;nh Ch&iacute;nh ph cho ph&eacute;p tnh c &aacute;p dng 2 phng &aacute;n  tng din t&iacute;ch t l&agrave;m loi h&igrave;nh nh&agrave;  n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<p>Theo kin ngh, ng Nai c&oacute; nhiu khu c&ocirc;ng nghip vi tr&ecirc;n 700.000 c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n, to nhiu &aacute;p lc cho a phng v vic &aacute;p ng nhu cu an sinh x&atilde; hi, c bit l&agrave; nhu cu nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi.</p>\r\n<p>Quy nh hin h&agrave;nh cho ph&eacute;p s dng mt phn qu t ti c&aacute;c khu nh&agrave;  thng mi  x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, trong thc t, ti ng Nai li c&oacute; nhiu d &aacute;n u t nh&agrave;  thng mi cao cp nhng vic b tr&iacute; nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi li kh&ocirc;ng hp l&yacute;.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_12/nha_dong_nai.jpg" alt="Dong Nai sap co them nhieu nha o xa hoi? hinh anh 1" width="660" height="420" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>ng Nai kin ngh tng din t&iacute;ch nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. nh minh ho:&nbsp;<em>L&ecirc; Qu&acirc;n.</em></h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo B X&acirc;y dng, quy nh v ph&aacute;t trin v&agrave; qun l&yacute; nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi ch cho ph&eacute;p ho&aacute;n i bng tin i vi phn din t&iacute;ch 20% trong c&aacute;c d &aacute;n nh&agrave;  thng mi c&oacute; quy m&ocirc; nh hn 10 ha.</p>\r\n<p>Thc t, qu t 20% nhn b&agrave;n giao t c&aacute;c d &aacute;n nh&agrave;  thng mi c&ograve;n nhiu im bt cp nh h tng x&atilde; hi c&ograve;n thiu, xa khu d&acirc;n c, xa nh&agrave; m&aacute;y n&ecirc;n cha ph&ugrave; hp  x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi cho c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n.</p>\r\n<p> trin khai c&oacute; hiu qu v&agrave; y nhanh c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi cho c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n, b n&agrave;y &atilde; kin ngh Ch&iacute;nh ph cho ph&eacute;p tnh ng Nai c x l&yacute;, ho&aacute;n i th&agrave;nh tin phn din t&iacute;ch 20% i vi c nhng d &aacute;n c&oacute; din t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n 10 ha.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, vic b&aacute;n u gi&aacute; qu t 20% nhn b&agrave;n giao t c&aacute;c d &aacute;n nh&agrave;  thng mi c&oacute; v tr&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng ph&ugrave; hp i  x&acirc;y nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi cng c cho ph&eacute;p xem x&eacute;t. Tin thu c s b sung v&agrave;o qu ph&aacute;t trin nh&agrave;   u t ph&aacute;t trin v&agrave; qun l&yacute; nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi ti v tr&iacute; kh&aacute;c thun li hn.</p>\r\n<p>B X&acirc;y dng cho rng ni dung kin ngh ca UBND tnh ng Nai l&agrave; ph&ugrave; hp vi c&aacute;c quy nh ca ph&aacute;p lut v nh&agrave; .</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, vic ho&aacute;n i bng qu t hoc bng tin, b&aacute;n u gi&aacute; qu t 20% i vi c&aacute;c d &aacute;n ph&aacute;t trin nh&agrave;  thng mi, d &aacute;n u t ph&aacute;t trin &ocirc; th c&oacute; quy m&ocirc; tr&ecirc;n 10 ha th&igrave; UBND tnh ng Nai phi b&aacute;o c&aacute;o Th tng  c xem x&eacute;t, chp thun i vi tng d &aacute;n c th.</p>\r\n</div>', '', '17881724.jpg', '17881724_300x200.jpg', 11, 1, '2017-08-18', '0000-00-00', 0),
(12, 0, 0, 'B trng Xy dng than kh lm nh  x hi v ci to chung c', '', '', '', 'bo-truong-xay-dung-than-kho-lam-nha-o-xa-hoi-va-cai-tao-chung-cu', '', '', '', 'Tr li cht vn cc i biu Quc hi, B trng Xy dng Phm Hng H  ch ra mt s kh khn trong xy dng nh  x hi v ci to cc chung c c.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">Tr li cht vn c&aacute;c i biu Quc hi, B trng X&acirc;y dng Phm Hng H&agrave; &atilde; ch ra mt s kh&oacute; khn trong x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi v&agrave; ci to c&aacute;c chung c c.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<p>S&aacute;ng 16/8, UB Thng v Quc hi t chc phi&ecirc;n cht vn B trng X&acirc;y dng Phm Hng H&agrave; mt s nh&oacute;m vn  trong v c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qun l&yacute; nh&agrave; nc ca B.</p>\r\n<h3>3 nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khin nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi gp kh&oacute;</h3>\r\n<p>Ti phi&ecirc;n cht vn, vic ci to c&aacute;c chung c c v&agrave; u t x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi c nhiu i biu quan t&acirc;m. i biu Lu B&igrave;nh Nhng cho bit Ch th s 03 ca Ch&iacute;nh ph &atilde; c&oacute; ni dung v vic x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  cho c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ti c&aacute;c khu c&ocirc;ng nghip, gim bt kh&oacute; khn. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nhiu a phng cha quan t&acirc;m n quy hoch, thm ch&iacute; quan t&acirc;m qu&aacute; n nh&agrave;  thng mi. i biu t c&acirc;u hi B X&acirc;y dng c&oacute; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch g&igrave;  ph&aacute;t trin nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi?</p>\r\n<p>Theo B trng Phm Hng H&agrave;, trong x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi ang tn ti mt s vn  cn c gii quyt.</p>\r\n<p>Th nht, ngun cung nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi ang rt thiu so vi nhu cu thc t.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Trong nhiu nm, vi n lc rt cao ch&uacute;ng ta mi c&oacute; 3,7 triu m2 nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. Trong khi nhu cu hin ti l&ecirc;n n hn 10 triu m2. Nh vy l&agrave; thiu rt nhiu&rdquo;, B trng H&agrave; nhn mnh.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_16/khu_do_thi_zing.jpg" alt="Bo truong Xay dung than kho lam nha o xa hoi va cai tao chung cu hinh anh 1" width="1920" height="1080" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">Thiu qu t l&agrave; mt trong nhng nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n c tr vic ph&aacute;t trin nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. nh:&nbsp;<em>Huy Nguyn.</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Th hai, mt s doanh nghip cha quan t&acirc;m nhiu n x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi do li nhun thp. Nh&agrave; nc cng c&oacute; mt s ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch u &atilde;i v vn, t ai&hellip; nhng li quy nh ch c li nhun ti a l&agrave; 10%. S li nhun n&agrave;y kh&aacute; thp, kh&ocirc;ng hp dn nhiu nh&agrave; u t.</p>\r\n<p>Trong quy hoch c&aacute;c khu &ocirc; th cng d&agrave;nh ra 20% qu t  nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, t x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi vn c&ograve;n rt hn ch. Thc t hin nay, mt s a phng cha quan t&acirc;m n t x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. Nhiu a phng thm ch&iacute; c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng b tr&iacute; , c bit l&agrave; x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  cho c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ti c&aacute;c khu c&ocirc;ng nghip, khu ch xut.</p>\r\n<p>Th ba, B trng H&agrave; n&ecirc;u ra thc trng thiu ngun lc v&agrave; c ch x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi.</p>\r\n<p>V c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p, ngi ng u B X&acirc;y dng cho bit cn c&oacute; s thay i cn bn  gii quyt vn  x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi. &ldquo; c&aacute;c nc th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng ph&acirc;n bit i tng v&agrave; cho vay mua nh&agrave;. Nh  M h cho vay vi l&atilde;i sut rt thp. H iu tit c&aacute;c khon thu kh&aacute;c  c&oacute; ngun lc  x&acirc;y dng. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ang nghi&ecirc;n cu c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p cn c l&acirc;u d&agrave;i hn  to t ph&aacute;t x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave;  x&atilde; hi&rdquo;, B trng H&agrave; n&oacute;i.</p>\r\n<h3>Doanh nghip kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; nhiu li &iacute;ch khi ci to chung c c</h3>\r\n<p>i biu Nguyn Tin Sinh (H&ograve;a B&igrave;nh) cho bit thc trng ngi d&acirc;n phi chu ni &aacute;m nh khi sng trong c&aacute;c chung c c xung cp. Thc trng hin nay, ngi d&acirc;n &atilde; t &yacute; ci to chung c c vi nhiu h&igrave;nh th&ugrave; k qu&aacute;i. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c quan chc nng li cha c&oacute; phng &aacute;n x l&yacute; c th chung c c. i biu t c&acirc;u hi v tr&aacute;ch nhim v&agrave; gii ph&aacute;p ca B trng Phm Hng H&agrave;.</p>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w660/Uploaded/iutmtn/2017_08_16/chung_cu_13_zing_1.JPG" alt="Bo truong Xay dung than kho lam nha o xa hoi va cai tao chung cu hinh anh 3" width="1980" height="1293" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">B&ecirc;n trong mt chung c c ti TP.HCM. nh:&nbsp;<em>L&ecirc; Qu&acirc;n.</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo B trng X&acirc;y dng Phm Hng H&agrave;, vn  ci to chung c c c&ograve;n tn ti nhiu vn . Theo &oacute;, li &iacute;ch Nh&agrave; nc, nh&agrave; u t v&agrave; ngi d&acirc;n cha c m bo, cha c&oacute; s h&agrave;i h&ograve;a n&ecirc;n cha th thng nht thc hin c.</p>\r\n<p>B trng cho bit bn cht vic x l&yacute; mt chung c c kh&ocirc;ng to ra c nhiu li &iacute;ch cho doanh nghip. iu &oacute; khin vic ci to chung c c ti c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph ln nh H&agrave; Ni v&agrave; TP.HCM din ra rt chm.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;R&agrave; so&aacute;t tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc hin nay c&oacute; khong 6.000 c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh chung c c 50-60 nm tui. Trong &oacute; c&oacute; hn 1.000 chung c thuc dng rt nguy him&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng H&agrave; nhn mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Theo B trng H&agrave;, cn x l&yacute; ki&ecirc;n quyt vn  ci to chung c c. Nu nh c&oacute; s c &aacute;ng tic ti mt chung c c n&agrave;o &oacute; s g&acirc;y ra thit hi rt ln.</p>\r\n<p>Trc tip i kho s&aacute;t nhiu c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ci to chung c c  H&agrave; Ni, theo B trng, hiu qu cho doanh nghip l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cao n&ecirc;n h kh&ocirc;ng mn m&agrave;.</p>\r\n<p>&Ocirc;ng cho rng cn i mi mt c&aacute;ch cn bn vn  chung c c vi nhng gii ph&aacute;p mi, t ph&aacute; hn. &ldquo;Theo quy nh ca ph&aacute;p lut, chung c &atilde; xung cp th&igrave; Nh&agrave; nc phi b tin ra  ci to. Qu thc ngun lc b&acirc;y gi l&agrave; rt kh&oacute;. Cn i mi cn bn&rdquo;, B trng H&agrave; nhn mnh.</p>\r\n</div>', '', '17135617.jpg', '17135617_300x200.jpg', 4, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 14),
(13, 0, 0, 'Metro Si Gn n nh cha chm', '', '', '', 'metro-sai-gon-no-nhu-chua-chom', '', '', '', 'Ti cuc hp v tnh hnh kinh t - x hi 7 thng u nm, Ch tch UBND TPHCM Nguyn Thnh Phong  ng  tm ng 500 t ng vn ngn sch tr n cho cc nh thu thi cng tuyn ng st  th (metro) s 1  trnh nguy c ln cng song s tin trn ch nh mui b bin.', '<p><strong>Chm vn, chm tin </strong></p>\r\n<p>Tuyn metro 1 d&agrave;i gn 20 km, i qua c&aacute;c qun 1, 2, 9, B&igrave;nh Thnh, Th c (TP HCM) v&agrave; huyn D An (B&igrave;nh Dng), trong &oacute; 2,6 km i ngm (3 nh&agrave; ga) v&agrave; hn 17 km i tr&ecirc;n cao (11 nh&agrave; ga). C&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh d kin a v&agrave;o khai th&aacute;c nm 2020. T&iacute;nh n cui th&aacute;ng 7, tuyn metro 1 (Bn Th&agrave;nh &ndash; Sui Ti&ecirc;n) &atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh 67,4% khi lng thi c&ocirc;ng vi chiu d&agrave;i 17,2 km. D kin trong th&aacute;ng 8/2017 c&aacute;c nh&agrave; thu s lp ng ray.</p>\r\n<p>Ph&oacute; ch tch UBND TPHCM L&ecirc; Thanh Li&ecirc;m cho bit nhu cu vn ODA ngun ng&acirc;n s&aacute;ch Trung ng cp ph&aacute;t giai on 2016-2020 cho d &aacute;n tuyn metro s 1 l&agrave; hn 20.900 t ng. UBND TPHCM &atilde; ba ln kin ngh Th tng b tr&iacute;  vn nhng B K hoch v&agrave; u t (KH&amp;T) mi b tr&iacute; 7.500 t cho d &aacute;n tuyn metro s 1. Vi s vn n&agrave;y, TPHCM ch &aacute;p ng c 39% nhu cu vn.</p>\r\n<p>Do kh&ocirc;ng m bo tin  thanh to&aacute;n theo hp ng n&ecirc;n mt s nh&agrave; thu &atilde; c&oacute; vn bn  ngh gi&atilde;n tin  thi c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; c&oacute; th s dng thi c&ocirc;ng nu tin  gii ng&acirc;n vn tip tc chm tr nh hin nay.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Trng ban Qun l&yacute; ng st &ocirc; th TPHCM L&ecirc; Nguyn Minh Quang, trong nm 2017, tuyn metro s 1 cn hn 5.400 t ng, trong khi vn Trung ng b tr&iacute; v th&agrave;nh ph l&agrave; 2.100 t ng. S tin tr&ecirc;n ch gn  tr n nh&agrave; thu (1.339 t ng) v&agrave; tin tm ng 900 t t ng&acirc;n s&aacute;ch ca UBND TPHCM  nh&agrave; thu thanh to&aacute;n lng, thng cho c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n v qu&ecirc; n Tt.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ang th&uacute;c nh&agrave; thu sm ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh tin  d &aacute;n c&agrave;ng sm c&agrave;ng tt. Nh&agrave; thu chp thun v&agrave; l&agrave;m quyt lit nhng h cng gay gt trong vic y&ecirc;u cu thanh to&aacute;n theo &uacute;ng tin  &ldquo;, &ocirc;ng Quang cho hay.</p>\r\n<p>Nghi&ecirc;m trng hn, t&igrave;nh trng &ldquo;git gu, v&aacute; vai&rdquo; trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh thc hin d &aacute;n tuyn metro s 1 &atilde; nh hng n nhiu d &aacute;n kh&aacute;c. &Ocirc;ng L&ecirc; Nguyn Minh Quang cho bit khi t vn  v t&agrave;i tr vn ODA cho mt s tuyn metro kh&aacute;c, C quan Hp t&aacute;c Quc t Nht Bn JICA n&oacute;i thng &ldquo;trc khi b&agrave;n chuyn &oacute; th&igrave; phi b&agrave;n vic thanh to&aacute;n&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;T thc t ca tuyn metro s 1, JICA rt quan ngi trong vic b tr&iacute; vn cho c&aacute;c d &aacute;n kh&aacute;c&hellip; C&aacute;c nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr rt bc x&uacute;c, cho rng tin h lo c nhng ch&uacute;ng ta b v&ograve;ng ln qun v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n c&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng Quang n&oacute;i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>N m &igrave;a, v&igrave; &acirc;u?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Theo &ocirc;ng Quang, vn  ln nht ca tuyn metro Bn Th&agrave;nh - Sui Ti&ecirc;n hin nay l&agrave; ph&acirc;n b vn t Trung ng. T th&aacute;ng 9/2016, B T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh &atilde; y&ecirc;u cu Kho bc Nh&agrave; nc kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n tip bi v&igrave; &atilde; thanh to&aacute;n vt vn ODA ca nm 2016.</p>\r\n<p>Th trng B KH&amp;T &agrave;o Quang Thu cho hay vn trung hn trong khong 300.000 t ng ca Trung ng th&igrave; &atilde; b tr&iacute; cho TPHCM 15.000 t ng. S tin n&agrave;y l&agrave; &atilde; ph&acirc;n b ht theo khu&ocirc;n kh ph&aacute;p l&yacute; ph&ecirc; duyt c&aacute;c d &aacute;n ca TPHCM.</p>\r\n<p>i vi tuyn metro s 1, trc kia Th tng ph&ecirc; duyt tng vn u t d &aacute;n l&agrave; 19.000 t ng nhng hin nay TPHCM  ngh tng l&ecirc;n 47.000 t ng. Vic tng vn gp gn 3 ln ban u cha c c quan c&oacute; thm quyn ph&ecirc; duyt. B KH&amp;T tip tc ph&acirc;n b vn l&agrave; vic chng ng ng  tr&aacute;nh c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ngng tr do ang thi c&ocirc;ng d dang.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ngh quyt s 49 ca Quc hi quy nh c&aacute;c d &aacute;n ang l&agrave;m hoc cha l&agrave;m nhng tng vn u t t 35.000 t ng tr l&ecirc;n l&agrave; d &aacute;n quan trng quc gia, phi b&aacute;o c&aacute;o Quc hi. D &aacute;n tuyn metro s 1 &atilde; tng l&ecirc;n 47.000 t ng ri, phi b&aacute;o c&aacute;o Quc hi cho ch trng ch c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng th&igrave; chc l&agrave; chu, kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m l&agrave;m&rdquo;, &ocirc;ng Thu n&oacute;i.</p>\r\n<p>Theo TS Nguyn B&aacute;ch Ph&uacute;c, Ch tch Hi T vn Khoa hc c&ocirc;ng ngh &amp; Qun l&yacute; TPHCM (HASCON), trc nm 2006, Quc hi &atilde; c&oacute; Ngh quyt 66, bt c d &aacute;n n&agrave;o c&oacute; vn u t tr&ecirc;n 20.000 t ng th&igrave; Ch&iacute;nh ph phi tr&igrave;nh b&aacute;o c&aacute;o nghi&ecirc;n cu tin kh thi  Quc hi xem x&eacute;t v&agrave; b phiu th&ocirc;ng qua Ngh quyt v ch trng u t.</p>\r\n<div id="admzone480458">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>Nm 2007, khi TPHCM tr&igrave;nh d &aacute;n n&agrave;y, tng d to&aacute;n c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh l&agrave; 1,09 t USD (tng ng 19.000 t ng), di mc 20.000 t ng Quc hi hn nh n&ecirc;n TPHCM ch cn tr&igrave;nh Th tng ph&ecirc; duyt.</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2010, Quc hi c&oacute; ngh quyt mi, n&acirc;ng mc 20.000 t l&ecirc;n 35.000 t ng, c&oacute; ngha, nhng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh tr&ecirc;n 35.000 t ng th&igrave; phi tr&igrave;nh Quc hi. TPHCM &atilde; iu chnh d &aacute;n v&agrave;o nm 2011, n&acirc;ng tng mc u t l&ecirc;n 2.49 t USD (tng ng 47.000 t ng), tng gp 2,4 ln so vi thi im ban u v&agrave; cao hn hn mc 35.000 t ng ca Quc hi nhng TPHCM li kh&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh Quc hi th&ocirc;ng qua. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt thiu s&oacute;t rt ln cn phi xem x&eacute;t mt c&aacute;ch nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>&aacute;ng n&oacute;i hn, sau khi iu chnh tng vn, TPHCM &atilde; cho khi c&ocirc;ng d &aacute;n v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 8/2012 khi Quc hi cha th&ocirc;ng qua ch trng u t.</p>\r\n<p>Theo UBND TPHCM, nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n d &aacute;n &ldquo;i vn&rdquo; l&agrave; do bin ng gi&aacute; nguy&ecirc;n - nhi&ecirc;n liu, t gi&aacute; ngoi hi, vic tng lng ti thiu t nm 2006 n 2009, u t u m&aacute;y, toa xe, trang thit b nh&agrave; ga, c&aacute;c trang thit b, h thng ti&ecirc;n tin... n&acirc;ng cao hiu qu khai th&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<blockquote class="summarize cms-quote">\r\n<div id="ObjectBoxContent_1502675968171" class="VCSortableInPreviewMode" dir="center" data-back="b0c4de" data-border="000000">\r\n<p><strong><em>&ldquo;T thc t ca tuyn metro s 1, JICA rt quan ngi trong vic b tr&iacute; vn cho c&aacute;c d &aacute;n kh&aacute;c&hellip;. C&aacute;c nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr rt bc x&uacute;c, cho rng tin h lo c nhng ch&uacute;ng ta b v&ograve;ng ln qun v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n c&rdquo;.</em></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote class="summarize cms-quote">\r\n<div id="ObjectBoxContent_1502678142531" class="VCSortableInPreviewMode" dir="center" data-back="E6E6FA" data-border="999">\r\n<p><strong>i vn</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i tuyn metro s 1, tuyn metro s 2 v&agrave; s 5 cng i vn rt cao so vi d to&aacute;n ban u. Theo Ban Qun l&yacute; ng st &ocirc; th, tuyn metro s 2 (Bn Th&agrave;nh - Tham Lng) ang c  xut iu chnh tng mc u t l&ecirc;n 2.152,36 triu USD (tng ng 47.605 t ng, tng khong 56,6% so vi tng mc u t c duyt nm 2010). Ba khon chi ph&iacute; tng mnh nht ti d &aacute;n n&agrave;y l&agrave; bi thng gii ph&oacute;ng mt bng tng t 119,38 triu USD l&ecirc;n 197,88 triu USD; x&acirc;y lp v&agrave; mua sm t 748,11 l&ecirc;n 1.198 t ng; chi ph&iacute; d ph&ograve;ng tng t 263 triu USD l&ecirc;n 368 triu USD.</p>\r\n<p>Ri&ecirc;ng tuyn s 5 (giai on 1) d&agrave;i gn 9 km (ng&atilde; t By Hin - Cu S&agrave;i G&ograve;n) khi ng k&yacute; danh mc d &aacute;n ODA ch c khong 833 triu EURO (nm 2011). Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, t&iacute;nh n nay tng mc u t d &aacute;n n&agrave;y c khong hn 1,5 t EURO (tng 87%). Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave;m thay i tng mc u t l&agrave; do t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n li khi lng to&agrave;n b d &aacute;n, b sung 5% chi ph&iacute; qun l&yacute; d &aacute;n, 7% chi ph&iacute; t vn x&acirc;y dng theo quy nh mi...</p>\r\n<p>&aacute;nh gi&aacute; v nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n i vn, Ban qun l&yacute; ng st &ocirc; th TP HCM cho rng do ch u t, c&aacute;c t vn lp d &aacute;n v&agrave; t vn thm tra trong nc cha c&oacute; kinh nghim, dn n vic t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n cha s&aacute;t thc t. C&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; x&acirc;y dng, gii ph&oacute;ng mt bng, qun l&yacute; d &aacute;n t&iacute;nh theo quy nh trong nc n&ecirc;n rt thp. ng thi do c&aacute;c d &aacute;n chm trin khai n&ecirc;n chu nh hng ca trt gi&aacute;, lm ph&aacute;t.</p>\r\n<p>Theo quy hoch &atilde; c Ch&iacute;nh ph ph&ecirc; duyt, TPHCM c&oacute; 8 tuyn metro gm: Tuyn s 1: Bn Th&agrave;nh - Sui Ti&ecirc;n d&agrave;i gn 20 km (d kin k&eacute;o d&agrave;i n B&igrave;nh Dng); Tuyn s 2: Th Thi&ecirc;m - Khu &ocirc; th T&acirc;y Bc C Chi khong 48 km (l&agrave;m trc on Bn Th&agrave;nh - Tham Lng).</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, tuyn 3A: Bn Th&agrave;nh - T&acirc;n Ki&ecirc;n khong 20 km; Tuyn 3B: Ng&atilde; s&aacute;u Cng H&ograve;a - Hip B&igrave;nh Phc d&agrave;i hn 12 km; Tuyn s 4A: Cu Bn C&aacute;t - Khu &ocirc; th Hip Phc d&agrave;i 36 km; Tuyn 4B: Ga C&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Gia nh - Ga Lng Cha C d&agrave;i 5,2 km; Tuyn s 5: Cu S&agrave;i G&ograve;n - bn xe Cn Giuc (khong 17 km); Tuyn s 6: B&agrave; Quo - v&ograve;ng xoay Ph&uacute; L&acirc;m (d&agrave;i hn 6 km).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>', '', '79306369.jpg', '79306369_300x200.jpg', 5, 1, '2017-08-18', '0000-00-00', 4),
(19, 0, 0, 'Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi dnh cho ngi tr', '', '', '', 'can-ho-45-m2-van-du-tien-nghi-danh-cho-nguoi-tre', '', '', '', 'Din tch ch 45 m2 nhng cn h  c thit k rt hp l vi y  tin nghi, gip ch nhn khng c cm gic sng trong khng gian eo hp.', '<p class="the-article-summary cms-desc">Din t&iacute;ch ch 45 m2 nhng cn h &atilde; c thit k rt hp l&yacute; vi y  tin nghi, gi&uacute;p ch nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; cm gi&aacute;c sng trong kh&ocirc;ng gian eo hp.</p>\r\n<div class="the-article-body cms-body">\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/1.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 1" width="1499" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h6>Cn h n&agrave;y l&agrave; ni sinh sng ca cp v chng tr v&agrave; mt ch&uacute; m&egrave;o.</h6>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/2.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 2" width="1498" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Nh&agrave; bao gm mt ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch lin bp, mt ph&ograve;ng ng, mt c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ph v&agrave; mt g&aacute;c x&eacute;p.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 3" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/3.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 3" width="1498" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Sofa c thit k quay lng li vi bp, to s t&aacute;ch bit cho hai kh&ocirc;ng gian.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 4" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/3a.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 4" width="665" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Bp n n gin vi b&agrave;n n va vn cho hai ngi.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 5" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/4.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 5" width="1498" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch s hu t s&aacute;ch ln &acirc;m tng.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 6" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/5.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 6" width="667" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Li v&agrave;o ph&ograve;ng ng dng ca k&eacute;o.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 7" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/6.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 7" width="704" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5> l&ecirc;n cu thang, ch nh&acirc;n cn h phi dch chuyn ca.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 8" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/7.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 8" width="667" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Cn h mang t&ocirc;ng trng  to cm gi&aacute;c rng hn so vi din t&iacute;ch thc.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 9" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/8.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 9" width="1504" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Cu thang dn l&ecirc;n g&aacute;c x&eacute;p.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 10" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/9.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 10" width="1498" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Ph&ograve;ng ng ca cn h s hu ca s ln.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img title="Cn h 45 m2 vn  tin nghi d&agrave;nh cho ngi tr h&igrave;nh nh 11" src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/10.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 11" width="1498" height="1000" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Ging ng c n&acirc;ng cao so vi s&agrave;n, ph&iacute;a di l&agrave; t  dng ngn k&eacute;o.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table class="picture" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pic"><img src="http://znews-photo-td.zadn.vn/w1024/Uploaded/ovhunut/2017_08_14/11.jpg" alt="Can ho 45 m2 van du tien nghi danh cho nguoi tre hinh anh 12" width="1498" height="1000" /><a class="btnSlideshow" href="http://news.zing.vn/can-ho-45-m2-van-du-tien-nghi-danh-cho-nguoi-tre-post771153.html#slideshow"><br /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="pCaption caption">\r\n<h5>Khi cn thit, ca trt ngn c&aacute;ch hai ph&ograve;ng c&oacute; th m rng ht c, gi&uacute;p vic di chuyn thun tin hn.</h5>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', '', '52076122.jpg', '52076122_300x200.jpg', 9, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 6);
