(15, 0, 0, 'Thm d n cn h condotel gia nhp th trng bt ng sn Nha Trang', '', '', '', 'them-du-an-can-ho-condotel-gia-nhap-thi-truong-bat-dong-san-nha-trang', '', '', '', 'D n cn h Scenia Bay (Nha Trang) vi 700 cn h  bn v hn 270 phng khch sn cho thu s chnh thc c ra mt trong qu 3 ny v d kin bn giao vo nm 2020.', '<p>Scenia Bay gm hn 700 cn h  b&aacute;n v&agrave; hn 270 ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch sn cho thu&ecirc;. c x&acirc;y dng tr&ecirc;n din t&iacute;ch 7.666 m2, d &aacute;n Scenia Bay ta lc ti s 25 &ndash; 26 Phm Vn ng (ng Trn Ph&uacute; k&eacute;o d&agrave;i), Tp Nha Trang. D &aacute;n c&oacute; bn mt tin hng ra: Phm Ngc Thch, Sao Bin, Nguyn Biu, mt ch&iacute;nh tip gi&aacute;p vi ng Phm Vn ng, l&agrave; con ng s&aacute;t bin Nha Trang.</p>\r\n<p>T Scenia Bay d d&agrave;ng di chuyn n nhng danh lam thng cnh p ti Nha Trang nh: H&ograve;n Mun, H&ograve;n Tm, Vnh Ninh V&acirc;n, Th&aacute;p B&agrave; Ponagar, H&ograve;n Chng, bin i L&atilde;nh, Ch m, o H&ograve;n R&ugrave;a, h&ograve;n Sn, ch&ugrave;a Long Sn&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ty c phn Nam Tin L&agrave;o Cai &ndash; ch u t d &aacute;n cn h Scenia Bay (Nha Trang) va k&yacute; kt hp t&aacute;c vi tp o&agrave;n kh&aacute;ch sn InVision Hospitality  qun l&yacute; vn h&agrave;nh to&agrave;n b d &aacute;n khi i v&agrave;o hot ng, d kin v&agrave;o nm 2020.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, C&ocirc;ng ty c phn Nam Tin L&agrave;o Cai tin th&acirc;n l&agrave; C&ocirc;ng ty x&acirc;y dng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh Nam Tin th&agrave;nh lp nm 1999 ti L&agrave;o Cai. C&ocirc;ng ty &atilde; c tnh giao thi c&ocirc;ng x&acirc;y dng mt s d &aacute;n nh: C&ocirc;ng trinh ng ai l&ocirc; Tr&acirc;n Hng ao, c&ocirc;ng trinh ke s&ocirc;ng h&ocirc;ng, ng QL4D, QL4E... D &aacute;n Tiu khu &ocirc; th s 1, Tiu khu &ocirc; th s 3, Tiu khu &ocirc; th s 5 thuc Khu &ocirc; th mi L&agrave;o Cai - Cam n; nh&agrave; m&aacute;y Thy in Ng&ograve;i Xanh; nh&agrave; m&aacute;y Thy in Minh Lng ...</p>', '', '87093562.jpg', '87093562_300x200.jpg', 7, 1, '2017-08-18', '0000-00-00', 3),
(16, 0, 1503074444, 'Nhng lu  vng khng th b qua khi lt sn g cho cn h chung c', '', '', '', 'nhung-luu-y-vang-khong-the-bo-qua-khi-lat-san-go-cho-can-ho-chung-cu', '', '', '', 'S dng g lt sn ang dn l s la chn hng u ca nhiu gia nh bi nhng tnh nng thit thc m n mang li. Tuy nhin,  sn nh lun bn v p theo thi gian th bn khng nn b qua nhng lu  c bit quan trng ny.', '<p>Ai cng bit rng s&agrave;n g c&oacute; nhng u im ni tri l&agrave; l&agrave;m cho cn nh&agrave; p hn bi c&aacute;c loi g c&oacute; m&agrave;u sc v&agrave; c&aacute;c loi v&acirc;n phong ph&uacute;, a dng. B mt g trn, b&oacute;ng v&agrave; mn gi&uacute;p cn nh&agrave; mang phong c&aacute;ch sang trng, hin i, sch s v&agrave; m&aacute;t m v m&ugrave;a h&egrave; m c&uacute;ng v m&ugrave;a &ocirc;ng, kh&ocirc; d&aacute;o khi tri nm.</p>\r\n<p> s dng &uacute;ng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t huy ht nhng u im bn, p, tin dng ca s&agrave;n g trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh l&aacute;t s&agrave;n bn c bit cn phi lu &yacute; nhng im sau.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H&atilde;y chc chn rng trc khi thi c&ocirc;ng s&agrave;n g mt s&agrave;n nh&agrave; bn phi bng phng</strong></p>\r\n<p>S&agrave;n g d&ugrave; l&agrave; s&agrave;n g t nhi&ecirc;n hay s&agrave;n g c&ocirc;ng nghip th&igrave; v bn cht kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; t&aacute;c dng chu lc. S n nh ca s&agrave;n g ph thuc v&agrave;o cht lng ca b mt nn b&ecirc;n di. Nhng loi b mt nn n nh  l&aacute;t s&agrave;n g l&agrave; nn b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng, nn xi mng, nn gch men.</p>\r\n<p>Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy vic u ti&ecirc;n trc khi lp t s&agrave;n g l&agrave; cn phi l&agrave;m tht phng mt s&agrave;n, loi b ht nhng g gh tr&ecirc;n mt. i vi nn b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng, xi mng n&ecirc;n c l&aacute;ng phng v&agrave; kh&ocirc; r&aacute;o, nhng im li tr&ecirc;n b mt nn sinh ra khi &aacute;nh va, b matit cn c loi b  tr&aacute;nh s&agrave;n g b p sau khi lp t.</p>\r\n<p>i vi nn gch men, nu cht lng l&aacute;t gch men k&eacute;m, nht l&agrave; ti c&aacute;c chung c mi, c&oacute; kh nng s&agrave;n gch men s b phng sau mt thi gian s dng nh hng n s&agrave;n g. Nu bn kh&ocirc;ng chc chn v im n&agrave;y, cn x l&yacute; ngay trc khi lp t s&agrave;n g.</p>\r\n<div class="VCSortableInPreviewMode">\r\n<div><img id="img_50416b50-823d-11e7-ad9d-299c2a54116c" src="http://cafefcdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/photo-1-1502858575692.jpg" alt="" data-original="http://cafefcdn.com/2017/photo-1-1502858575692.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="PhotoCMS_Caption">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n l&aacute;t s&agrave;n g th&ocirc;ng ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; qu&aacute; s&aacute;t m&eacute;p tng</strong></p>\r\n<p>S&agrave;n g c&oacute; th b gi&atilde;n n trong c&aacute;c iu kin thi tit, nhit  kh&aacute;c nhau. V&igrave; vy, mt lu &yacute; khi lp t s&agrave;n g c&ocirc;ng nghip l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n l&aacute;t th&ocirc;ng ph&ograve;ng m&agrave; cn ngt mch h gia c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng  b&ugrave; gi&atilde;n n.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, vi m&eacute;p g ca h&agrave;ng u ti&ecirc;n s&aacute;t vi tng, cn lp t c&aacute;ch 10mm n 12mm  to khong h b&ugrave; gi&atilde;n n cho g. Nu kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; b&ugrave; gi&atilde;n n s l&agrave;m cho s&agrave;n b phng, v&ecirc;nh l&ecirc;n, mt thm m ca ph&ograve;ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ch l&agrave;m s&agrave;n g khi &atilde; lp xong ca v&agrave; sn tng</strong></p>\r\n<p> tr&aacute;nh nhng t&aacute;c ng xu t thi tit nh ma nng ht v&agrave;o nh hng n s&agrave;n g bn ch n&ecirc;n lp t s&agrave;n g khi &atilde; ho&agrave;n thin ca hoc ca s th&ocirc;ng ra ngo&agrave;i tri. Ngo&agrave;i ra, vic lp t s&agrave;n g n&ecirc;n l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng on cui c&ugrave;ng trc khi sn  tr&aacute;nh th thi c&ocirc;ng sn i li hoc va qut v&agrave;o s&agrave;n g g&acirc;y try xc v&agrave; l&agrave;m bn s&agrave;n nh&agrave;.</p>\r\n<div id="admzone480458">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="VCSortableInPreviewMode IMSCurrentEditorEditObject">\r\n<div><img id="img_4fa94a00-823d-11e7-94d2-eff83e0e2084" src="http://cafefcdn.com/2017/photo-2-1502858575695.jpg" alt="" data-original="http://cafefcdn.com/2017/photo-2-1502858575695.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="PhotoCMS_Caption">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Cn chn vt liu ph kin ph&ugrave; hp cho s&agrave;n g  c&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng gian kh&aacute;c nhau</strong></p>\r\n<p>Lp l&oacute;t s&agrave;n g th&ocirc;ng thng i vi s&agrave;n g c&ocirc;ng nghip l&agrave; xp nilon 3mm, i vi s&agrave;n g t nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; xp nilon tr&aacute;ng bc hay phom cao su non. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nu bn l&aacute;t s&agrave;n g ti tng 1 c&oacute; nguy c nm m cao th&igrave; n&ecirc;n s dng xp nilon tr&aacute;ng bc hay phom cao su non d&ugrave; l&agrave; s&agrave;n g c&ocirc;ng nghip. Tng t l&agrave; vt liu ph&agrave;o ch&acirc;n tng, ph&agrave;o nha hay ph&agrave;o laminate c&oacute;  bn v&agrave; t&iacute;nh chu nc cao n&ecirc;n c s dng nu tng c&oacute; kh nng b m c&ograve;n ph&agrave;o th&ocirc;ng dng tr&ecirc;n th trng th&igrave; kh nng chng m kh&ocirc;ng cao.</p>\r\n<p><strong>K&iacute;ch thc ca thanh g cn ph&ugrave; hp vi tng kh&ocirc;ng gian</strong></p>\r\n<p>S&agrave;n g cng gi&uacute;p ni rng hoc thu hp kh&ocirc;ng gian cn ph&ograve;ng. Vi nhng cn ph&ograve;ng nh, hp, bn n&ecirc;n la chn s&agrave;n g vi nhng ming gh&eacute;p nh v&agrave; s&aacute;ng m&agrave;u. Ngc li, nhng cn ph&ograve;ng rng n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng nhng ming gh&eacute;p to, c&oacute; v&acirc;n ln v&agrave; ti m&agrave;u  ph&ograve;ng dng nh gn, mang n cm gi&aacute;c m m hn</p>', '', '10958528.jpg', '10958528_300x200.jpg', 8, 1, '2017-08-18', '2017-08-18', 21);
