(40, 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 'im mnh ca cty TNHH bt ng sn XYZ', '', '', '', 'diem-manh-cua-cty-tnhh-bat-dong-san-xyz', 0, '', 'Trong thi im hin nay, t cc  th ln n cc  th loi TB v nh, nh ph, bit th xy dng trong d n trn t chia l chim t l kh ln trong tng s cc cng trnh c xy dng. Vi c im tng t nhau v tng th kin trc, bi cnh, im nhn ca mi cng trnh ph thuc rt ln  cht lng ca bn v thit k. Nhu cu thit k cho cc i tng trn ngy cng tr nn cn thit, tuy nhin cc c nhn, h kinh doanh v ch d n lun gp phi vn  kh khn  l s thiu chuyn nghip trong cc bn thit k, th tc v thi gian hon thnh chm, mc chi ph thit k cao trong khi cht lngh s khng c m bo.', '<p><em><span>Trong thi im hin nay, t c&aacute;c &ocirc; th ln n c&aacute;c &ocirc; th loi TB v&agrave; nh, nh&agrave; ph, bit th x&acirc;y dng trong d &aacute;n tr&ecirc;n t chia l&ocirc; chim t l kh&aacute; ln trong tng s c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh c x&acirc;y dng. Vi c im tng t nhau v tng th kin tr&uacute;c, bi cnh, im nhn ca mi c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ph thuc rt ln  cht lng ca bn v thit k. Nhu cu thit k cho c&aacute;c i tng tr&ecirc;n ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng tr n&ecirc;n cn thit, tuy nhi&ecirc;n c&aacute;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, h kinh doanh v&agrave; ch d &aacute;n lu&ocirc;n gp phi vn  kh&oacute; khn &oacute; l&agrave; s thiu chuy&ecirc;n nghip trong c&aacute;c bn thit k, th tc v&agrave; thi gian ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh chm, mc chi ph&iacute; thit k cao trong khi cht lngh s kh&ocirc;ng c m bo.</span></em></p>\r\n<p>Th&ocirc;ng thng, i vi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty x&acirc;y dng hin nay, bn v thit k l&agrave; mt phn thuc dch v trn g&oacute;i bao gm c: t vn thit k , gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t, x&acirc;y dng&hellip; Do vy, c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty x&acirc;y dng ng thi l&agrave; c&aacute;c nh&agrave; thu x&acirc;y dng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; s u t nhiu cho mng bn v thit k. C&aacute;c h s thit k bit th hoc nh&agrave; ph  HN v&agrave; TP HCM c&oacute; cht lng tt thng dao ng khong 50 &ndash; 70 triu cho c&aacute;c cn nh&agrave; c&oacute; din t&iacute;ch x&acirc;y dng t 200-300 m2 . C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty TVTK ch thc hin thit k s ph&aacute;c 1 n 2 ln  kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng la chn phng &aacute;n .Vn  v kt cu, k thut cn nh&agrave; khi thit k cha c tri qua t&iacute;nh bn vng trong thc t , thi gian thc hin h s k&eacute;o d&agrave;i TB t 2 n 3 th&aacute;ng. Cha t&iacute;nh thi gian ph&aacute;t sinh nhiu vn  nh ph&aacute;p l&yacute;, c&aacute;c thay i kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Ri&ecirc;ng i vi nhng c&aacute; nh&acirc;n  c&aacute;c tnh, TP kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc, mun s hu nhng b h s thit k vi cht lng cao cp phi chp nhn b ra khon ph&iacute; ln hn nhiu  thu&ecirc; Kin tr&uacute;c s thit k hoc v&agrave;o TP ln  t&igrave;m n c&aacute;c n v t vn thit k chuy&ecirc;n nghip . Nhng iu n&agrave;y cng cha thc s tha m&atilde;n v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng c la chn ht nhng mu nh&agrave; p v&agrave; ph&ugrave; hp vi s th&iacute;ch ca c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n trong gia &igrave;nh . Mi c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ch 1 n 2 ln x&acirc;y dng nh&agrave; cho m&igrave;nh trong i v&igrave; vy la chn ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c s th&iacute;ch ca m&igrave;nh l&agrave; iu rt quan trng .</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.vietbaipr.com/upload/vietbaipr/product/biet-thu2.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Mua bn quyn thit k &ndash; xu hng la chn mi cho nh&agrave; ph, bit th</p>\r\n<p>Nhm khc phc nhng hn ch &oacute;, ng thi to iu kin cho mi c&aacute; nh&acirc;n u c&oacute; th s hu c nhng b h s thit k cao cp, C&ocirc;ng ty x&acirc;y dng KT thuc tp o&agrave;n BS Nam Long a ra gii ph&aacute;p &ldquo; b&aacute;n bn quyn thit k&rdquo; cho c&aacute;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, h KD, ch d &aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p>Vi chi ph&iacute; ch 10 &ndash; 20 triu, c&aacute;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n s c s hu mt b h s bn quyn thit k chuy&ecirc;n nghip, vi nhng bn v chi tit l&ecirc;n ti 200 trang bao gm: ni tht, kt cu, h thng in, nc v&agrave; 1 bn d to&aacute;n chi tit.</p>\r\n<p>Do c&oacute; s u t c bit cho mng thit k, C&ocirc;ng ty KT c&oacute; khong hn 200 mu kin tr&uacute;c thit k nh&agrave; ph, bit th tng ng vi d&ograve;ng kin tr&uacute;c hin i, hu hin i, c in, HiTech&hellip; KH c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y &yacute; la chn trong &ldquo;ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng&rdquo; nhng mu thit k  c&oacute; mt mu ph&ugrave; hp cho ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; ca m&igrave;nh theo s th&iacute;ch, phong c&aacute;ch y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c mu thit k hu ht l&agrave; sn phm BS c tri nghim qua thc t c&aacute;c d &aacute;n ca KTcorp &atilde; thc hin trong v&ograve;ng 7 nm ti TP.HCM v&agrave; c&aacute;c tnh th&agrave;nh kh&aacute;c . Do vy, c&aacute;c vn  v kt cu v&agrave; k thut ca c&aacute;c mu nh&agrave; c m bo trong chun quy phm v kt cu cng nh c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chun k thut kh&aacute;c .</p>\r\n<p>Tng ng vi c&aacute;c mu nh&agrave; la chn KH c&oacute; th thay i m&agrave;u sc, VLXD cng nh c&aacute;c n gi&aacute; ph&ugrave; hp theo nhu cu. Do vy, KH s ch ng c v t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.vietbaipr.com/upload/vietbaipr/product/194438625_27.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>KTcorp cng hn ch ti a c&aacute;c th tc v&agrave; thi gian cho KH. Nh &oacute;, thi gian ch i t 2 -3 th&aacute;ng c r&uacute;t xung g&oacute;i gn trong v&ograve;ng 1 tun.</p>\r\n<p>Nhm to iu kin thun li cho nhng KH ngo&agrave;i TP HCM, c&ocirc;ng ty KT se&otilde; bo&aacute; tr&iacute; kha&ugrave;ch sa&iuml;n mie&atilde;n ph&iacute; ta&iuml;i d&ouml;&iuml; a&ugrave;n co&acirc;ng ty. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute; KT cng h tr c&aacute;c KH nu c&oacute; nhu cu x&acirc;y dng. Theo &oacute;, KH s c u ti&ecirc;n 1, 8 triu ng cho phn th&ocirc;. 2, 8 triu cho phn ho&agrave;n thin. KH s c h tr vay t 30% &ndash; 50% GTH trong v&ograve;ng 3- 6 th&aacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh l&atilde;i sut v&agrave; c min ph&iacute; thit k nu x&acirc;y dng theo chng tr&igrave;nh bn quyn thit k ca c&ocirc;ng ty .</p>', 1, 1, 1502895635, 0, 0);
